{{vgname|魔幻歷險|en=Adventure}}是一個在1979年發行<ref name="JaggedInterview">{{cite web | last = Connelly | first = Joey | title = Interview with Warren Robinett | publisher = The Jadded Gamer | url = http://www.thejadedgamer.net/interview_warrenrobinett.shtml | accessdate = 2007-10-11 }}</ref>，在[[雅達利2600|雅達利2600]]上運行的[[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]]，被認為是[[電子遊戲歷史|電子遊戲歷史]]上第一個動作冒險遊戲<ref name="WarrenSite">{{cite web | last = Robinett | first = Warren | title = Adventure for the Atari 2600 Video Game Console | url = http://www.warrenrobinett.com/adventure/index.html | accessdate = 2007-10-11 | archive-date = 2012-08-13 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/69tgFu8GI?url=http://www.warrenrobinett.com/adventure/index.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。编写它的程序员Warren Robinett在遊戲中引入了一個廣為人知的[[彩蛋_(視覺)|彩蛋]]<ref name="gamespot">{{cite web | last = Gouskos | first = Carrie | title = The Greatest Easter Eggs in Gaming | url = http://www.gamespot.com/features/6131572/index.html | accessdate = 2008-01-30 | archive-date = 2007-10-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071020104450/http://www.gamespot.com/features/6131572/index.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，在很长一段时间内被认为是电子游戏世界中的第一个彩蛋<ref>{{Cite web|title=整整40年后，我们终于看到了游戏史上第一个彩蛋 - 触乐|url=http://www.chuapp.com/article/282609.html|accessdate=2021-01-01|work=www.chuapp.com}}</ref>。

